"title": "8410: decision-making, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8410",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides examples of good and bad decision-making, as well as offering guidance as to how decisions ought to be made.</p>\n<h2>Examples of good decision-making</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:15\">JOS 24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:8-Gen13:9\">GEN 13:8–13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:2-Gen35:4\">GEN 35:2–35:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:24-Exod18:25\">EXO 18:24–18:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:26\">EXO 32:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:15-Ruth1:16\">RUT 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:6-1Sam14:7\">1SA 14:6–14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:4-1Sam24:7\">1SA 24:4–24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:21-Neh4:23\">NEH 4:21–4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:15-Esth4:16\">EST 4:15–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:8\">DAN 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:18\">DAN 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:19-Matt4:20\">MAT 4:19–4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38-Luke10:42\">LUK 10:38–10:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:36-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:36–4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:35-Acts5:39\">ACT 5:35–5:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:25-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:25–11:26</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad decision-making</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10-Gen12:13\">GEN 12:10–12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:10-Gen13:11\">GEN 13:10–13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:1-Gen16:3\">GEN 16:1–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:1-Exod32:4\">EXO 32:1–32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:31\">NUM 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:1-Num16:3\">NUM 16:1–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21\">JOS 7:21</a> <em>Achan disobeyed the LORD's instructions</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:23-Judg8:27\">JDG 8:23–8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:3\">JDG 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:1\">JDG 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:8-1Sam13:9\">1SA 13:8–13:9</a> <em>Saul made the offering in Samuel's absence</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:4\">2SA 11:2–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:8-1Kgs12:15\">1KI 12:8–12:15</a> <em>Rehoboam followed bad advice</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:1\">2KI 24:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:5\">HOS 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:3\">JON 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22\">MRK 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:2\">ACT 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:27\">ACT 24:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:16\">MAT 26:14–26:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:10-Mark14:11\">MRK 14:10–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:4-Luke22:6\">LUK 22:4–22:6</a> <em>Judas decided to betray Jesus Christ for money</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:1\">MRK 15:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:1-Matt27:2\">MAT 27:1–27:2</a> <em>the decision to put Jesus Christ to death</em></p>\n<h2>The sovereignty of God in decision-making</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:19-Gen50:20\">GEN 50:19–50:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:8\">GEN 45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:13\">NUM 24:13</a> <em>Balaam could only curse or bless at the LORD's bidding</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:39-Judg6:40\">JDG 6:39–6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:4\">JDG 14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:25\">1SA 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:20\">2CH 25:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13-Ps103:14\">PSA 103:13–103:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:25-Joel2:26\">JOL 2:25–2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:8-Mic7:9\">MIC 7:8–7:9</a>ACT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:23-Mic2:24\">2:23–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:28\">ACT 4:27–4:28</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a></p>\n<h2>Decisions have to be made</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:19-Deut30:20\">DEU 30:19–30:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:30\">EZK 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:17\">MAT 27:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:21\">MAT 27:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38-Acts2:40\">ACT 2:38–2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30-Acts16:31\">ACT 16:30–16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:15-2Cor1:17\">2CO 1:15–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:2\">GAL 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Good decision-making involves consideration for others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:16-Job31:23\">JOB 31:16–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">ISA 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3\">JER 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:14-Amos5:15\">AMO 5:14–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13-Matt5:16\">MAT 5:13–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:35-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:35–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>All decision-making must be subject to the will of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:13–4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:42\">MAT 26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>",
